            <p class="">3. Notwithstanding anything contained herein, the Instructor does not have the right to assign any of his/her duties or obligations under this Agreement.</p>

            <p class="py-md-1">4. The Instructor undertakes to maintain a healthy and professional working relationship with the Learner.</p>

            <p class="py-md-1">5. The Instructor shall comply with all applicable laws in the course of performing its obligations under this Agreement.</p>

            <p class="py-md-1">6. The Instructor agrees, affirms, acknowledges and understands that he is in no way covered by either the Learner or LYVYO in any matter(s) of insurance and will take out, should he deem appropriate, his own insurance policy in respect of any personal and/or third party claims.</p>

            <p class="pt-md-3">7. The Instructor warrants that all information given to the Learner (via LYVYO or otherwise) whether prior to, during the provision of the services envisaged under this Agreement, as well as post the services have been tendered are true and accurate in all respects. For clarification of doubt, the information envisaged herein shall include any and all information that the Instructor provides to LYVYO on an ongoing basis.</p>

            <p class="py-md-1">8. The Instructor represents that he/she has no criminal antecedents or convictions and/ or any criminal action is pending against him/her LYVYO reserves the right to request a criminal background check at the cost of the Instructor.</p>

            <p class="py-md-1">9. The Instructor specifically represents and warrants that he is proficient in handling each and every aspect of technology which is required to carry out any and all functions under this Agreement.</p>

            <p class="py-md-1">10. The Instructor specifically represents and warrants he has access to a stable internet connection and adequate infrastructure such as computer, microphone, etc. necessary for due completion of any and all of his obligations under this Agreement. Refer to Annexure A for minimum technical requirements to become a LYVYO Instructor.</p>

            <p class="py-md-1">11. The Instructor shall only work in quiet, ambient surroundings amenable to a healthy conversation while taking any Session.</p>


            <h5 class="font-dubai-bold pt-md-2 ">7. EVENTS OF DEFAULT</h5>
